{"tid":515080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Angelababy拍吻戲要隔住保鮮紙？　劇組發聲明讚演員專業","createTime":"2017-12-31T06:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T19:13:32.000Z","uid":156068,"like":3,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe092a9dca392c731bf46a6b49e4d1507e4580f","tid":515080,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"網上的傳言指baby結婚後，朱唇只會留給老公黃曉明，不能接受老公以外的男人碰她，所以不會跟其他演員拍接吻戲，就算要拍也不會真錫，而是要隔住一塊膠膜。對於網民的質疑，baby的工作室，指該言論是惡意抹黑baby的職業道德，對此他們絕不姑息，更不排除採取法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n《創業時代》的劇組方亦發出聲明，指出「在拍攝期間，演員一律嚴格遵循道演的安排和要求，認真完成每一次拍攝，近日某大號發文baby被爆與黃軒拍吻戲隔着保鮮膜，此消息純屬造謠，我們歡迎社會各界的監督，但惡意抹黑的言論，我們也將堅決的抵制。」劇組方面力撐baby專業，而近日官方釋出的劇集預告片，亦確實看不到吻戲時有膠片存在，至於baby是否被抹黑，答案已經呼之欲出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/143612_e01f8c291662314839c43bd9046e6a1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F143612_e01f8c291662314839c43bd9046e6a1f.jpg&h=afa52dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/143619_40536d144c110e01827f371aa681f878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F143619_40536d144c110e01827f371aa681f878.jpg&h=112b026a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/143620_8ef655e1a7d04153eac5a30073b7d266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F143620_8ef655e1a7d04153eac5a30073b7d266.jpg&h=04e9dd1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/143624_4a9420621ebb4403e2b5cbe0a604b13b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F143624_4a9420621ebb4403e2b5cbe0a604b13b.jpg&h=ea98719e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52c0af1aa2a80c8ac7e4f0402f99cea1d345a301","tid":515080,"uid":87573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"